{"tid":2079893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"71維園不見，將來都唔會再有得見","createTime":"2020-06-26T05:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:04:23.000Z","uid":289654,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d8e1603c09222f63bf187ff38157f9fdc7c66b","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1qiXWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1qiXWg.jpg&h=a23026de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論有無不反<br />\n大家都要出黎<br />\n你可能會話送頭<br />\n你可能會話無用<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n你記住<br />\n今個71唔出<br />\n你以後都唔會再有機會出<br />\n<br />\n遊行，集會，罷工<br />\n本身就係我哋去表達意見既權利<br />\n上年，我地香港人表現出無窮既鬥志去反送中<br />\n今年，我地香港人更加要企硬唔要國安法<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n真係希望睇緊連登既你<br />\n無論係學生，年青人，啱啱有家室，定係中產，銀髮族<br />\n71一定要出黎<br />\n同叫埋你身邊一齊出黎<br />\n呢個係我地面對極權既戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家幫推，俾更多人見到"},{"pid":"f13a5db1e9db5b5683997f1e39d52d0b3dc94b88","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"68de8ea316c45927f377b6bb97a51179c7bca101","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"力推"},{"pid":"ef0c0664486a52135e7c9ac66b85b983f8f17bab","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"有多啲人見到"},{"pid":"2778fb66df609204e5797aa06ceee034b323508b","tid":2079893,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"幫推 順便<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">攬炒團隊</span></span>聯繫到喺EU有一定影響力嘅Martens Centre think tank 討論歐盟可以點支援香港！<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓：<br />\n#斯洛伐克前總理 Mikul&aacute;&scaron; Dzurinda、#歐洲議會議員 Miriam Lexmann MEP、#梁繼平 手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時間：<br />\n26/6 (五) 香港時間1645-1745</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/events/s/hong-kong-under-the-dragons-br/713316162815311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fevents%2Fs%2Fhong-kong-under-the-dragons-br%2F713316162815311&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=aaf8ccc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/events/s/hong-kong-under-the-dragons-br/713316162815311</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbVyMMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbVyMMe.jpg&h=8f0dca4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【626攬炒團隊 歐盟戰線新嘗試！】</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2079331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2079331</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">時間上，明白大家返緊工，未必衝到去廁格睇直播。但希望大家可以喺夜晚、週末重溫支持，借力量俾我地。<br />\n<br />\n今次 think tank 活動view 數將會係一大指標，鼓勵更多歐洲think tanks 為香港發聲，思考香港重光後嘅國際價值。626見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e8b991974a9327a8b0a9bdb33872cf4126171da","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a56ab9d2cf967b3a13c7fa680ce489891b22f025","tid":2079893,"uid":58789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa2bb3193acdc3c1f40a2e9f199117ed7b815c6b","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"#71"},{"pid":"850c0b0d92a9b1443d706a756cc94bf810a56b23","tid":2079893,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"#維國見"},{"pid":"741c0a76041a4dcf4ba092c75ff084cadd41f87c","tid":2079893,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=